PLACEHOLDER: id_mapping_flow.png

Create a flowchart showing the ID↔Name mapping workflow:
1. Node start
2. Call GetDataDescriptionList()
3. Parse 7 asset types (RigidBody, Skeleton, ForcePlate, Device, Asset, MarkerSet, Camera)
4. Build assetNameToAssetID map
5. Build assetIDToAssetName map
6. User parameter 'rigid_name' → lookup ID
7. Incoming frame with ID → lookup Name → verify → publish

Style: Flowchart with decision diamonds and process boxes
Tools: draw.io or Mermaid
Resolution: 1200px width, PNG format
